summary:
- **Cessation of Securities**: 11,319,488 ordinary shares (DNL) cancelled under an on-market buy-back on 23/06/2025.  
- **Buy-Back Details**: Part of an ongoing on-market buy-back program of up to AUD 400 million (consideration paid for this tranche: AUD 30,368,368.58).  
- **Post-Cessation Issued Capital**: 1,842,454,876 ordinary shares (DNL) remain on issue.
